Step 1: Copy the activecollab-timer/ directory into /opt
This will end up being /opt/activecollab-timer/

Step 2: Create /usr/share/applications/activecollab-timer.desktop and append the following content
[Desktop Entry]
Name=ActiveCollab-Timer
Exec=activecollab-timer
Terminal=false
Type=Application
Icon=/opt/activecollab-timer/timer-128.png
Categories=TextEditor;IDE;Development
X-Ayatana-Desktop-Shortcuts=NewWindow
 
[NewWindow Shortcut Group]
Name=New Window

Step 3: In your ~/.bash_profile, append /opt/activecollab-timer to your $PATH

Step 4: Re-log into your system
